                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for recovering alcohol in metallographic laboratory waste liquid",
                    "一种金相实验室废液中酒精的回收方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for recovering alcohol in metallographic laboratory waste liquid, which comprises the following steps: firstly, respectively and independently storing nitric acid alcohol corrosion waste liquid and alcohol cleaning waste liquid in a metallographic laboratory, and purifying and recovering alcohol through the processes of oxidation, precipitation, filtration, neutralization, distillation and the like by utilizing the characteristic that the content of iron ions and hydrogen ions in the corrosion waste liquid is higher; meanwhile, by utilizing the characteristics that the cleaning waste liquid contains oil stains, iron mud and pigments, the alcohol is purified by means of filtration, purification, distillation and the like; according to the technical scheme, the alcohol in the metallographic laboratory corrosion waste liquid can be efficiently recycled, the purity of the recycled alcohol can reach 95% or above, the process operation is simple, the waste liquid recycling rate is high, and the good promotion effect on energy conservation, emission reduction, cost reduction and efficiency improvement of a laboratory can be achieved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种金相实验室废液中酒精的回收方法，该方法首先将金相实验室中硝酸酒精腐蚀废液、酒精清洗废液分别单独存放，利用腐蚀废液中铁离子、氢离子较高的特点，通过氧化、沉淀、过滤、中和、蒸馏等过程，实现酒精的提纯和回收；同时利用清洗废液中含油污、铁泥、色素较高的特点，通过过滤、净化、蒸馏等手段实现酒精的提纯；通过上述技术方案可实现金相实验室腐蚀废液中酒精的高效回收利用，回收酒精的纯度可达到95％以上，其过程操作简单、废液回收利用率高，能够对实验室节能减排、降本增效起到良好的推动作用。"
                }
            ]
        }
